      • getCompression

        @NotNull
public FileEntity.CompressionType getCompression()
        Get the compression type for the data. This method is intended for use by the FileSystemDAO implementation. The FileSystemDAO.getStream(FileEntity) method handles uncompressing the stream, code outside of the file system should always assume streams are uncompressed.
        Returns:
        FileEntity.CompressionType.
